<h2 class="bold font-l">K-On!</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
After sleeping in, Yui rushes her way to school so she isn't late, but not before grabbing some breakfast. </p>
<p class='example_row'>Example of:<br><a href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/ToastOfTardiness" class='trope-example-link'>Toast of Tardiness</a></p>
